{
  "stem": "21139.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't-- I don't even remember my schoolmates in Konigsbach.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One writes to me now, since last year, and I have no idea who she is.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He lived a different direction away from us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He lived-- it was not very far from the train station.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we lived a little bit away from there, not too far.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was within walking distance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How would-- what could he do to make you say heil Hitler when you would meet in the street?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Just to look at me, that's all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was-- he wanted this as a greeting to him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To-- to humiliate me, I suppose, because although-- I was very young, but as the years went by and I thought about it and this is I presumed the purpose of his-- his treatment.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not easy, because there were already the Hitler years and we lived always in fear.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't-- I never had a childhood, because there was always the news, the speeches about Hitler.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't understand what it was all about, but I could feel the tension.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we couldn't go out to play with other children or ride a bicycle the way we would have liked to do.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So my youngest brother Siegie and I, we were mostly in our garden playing there with mud, making mud pies and things like this.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or my mother used to give us [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a cup, two cups, one with sugar in it and one with water in it so we could wash the berries first and put them then in sugar, so we-- for the treat, as a treat for us.",
      "word_count": 49
    }
  ],
